# Smart Parking Sensor

## Components
- Arduino Uno
- HC-SR04 Ultrasonic Sensor
- OLED Display
- 3 LEDs
- Buzzer

## Connections
- TRIG -> D9
- ECHO -> D10
- SDA -> A4
- SCL -> A5
- Red LED -> D2
- Yellow LED -> D3
- Green LED -> D4
- Buzzer -> D6

## Formula
Distance = (Time × Speed of Sound) / 2

## Working
The ultrasonic sensor measures the distance to an obstacle. The OLED displays the distance, LEDs indicate the safety zone, and the buzzer warns when an object is too close.
